     0.  (Contributed by Paul Chapman, 21-Mar-2011.) $)
  gcd0val $p |- ( 0 gcd 0 ) = 0 $=
    ( vn cc0 cgcd co wceq wa cv cdivides wbr cz crab cr clt csup cif wcel 0z
    gcdval mp2an eqid iftrue eqtri ) BBCDZBBEZUDFZBAGBHIZUFFAJKLMNZOZBBJPZUIUCU
